ądów. Pokazali na co ich stać. ', 'media_src': 'https://bi.im-g.pl/im/49/8d/15/z22598729V.jpg', 'media_desc': '', 'media_type': 'image', 'comments': []}, 'timestamp': 1563289362.953665}}